{
  "stem": "17426.7",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Our commandant at this time, Max Schmidt, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] who took over from Otto Moll when Otto Moll was sent to the east to organize the destruction of Treblinka and Sobibor and the other camps.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "He took us out of Dora.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "While the other inmates that were in Dora before us were left and were liberated, the 600 or so that we were from Auschwitz, he took us out, put us on barges, on flat barges, on the Elbe, and brought us all the way north to Hamburg.",
      "word_count": 47
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was quite openly talked about.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Some of the electricians and even the workers that we worked with were sabotaging their work.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When we were assigned to a group of Frenchmen, mostly French and Russian-- and some Polish people were there too.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It wasn't per se a strictly Jewish camp.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "This was sort of like an international camp.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Some of them, those Russians-- those French people that we worked with, they told us to just take the-- we were supposed to clean parts and put them from one barrel into the other.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they said, don't clean them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Just do whatever.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "If somebody comes by, try to clean them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But don't put them in the other barrel.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Put them back in the same barrel.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So the work was obviously not done anymore.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And some of the electricians were-- understand-- I understand, were crossing wires and doing all kind of sabotage.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So from that point on that we came in-- in April there, and very few-- I only saw two or three V weapons leave the [GERMAN], leave the-- the-- the-- the Harz mountains.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "What were the conditions like of this camp?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were in a separate camp, in a-- in a block.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
